/eps-svg/FactorialOld_1000.svg" alt=3D"FactorialOld"> (Jarrett
 1830; Jarrett 1831; Mellin 1909; Lewin 1958, p.&nbsp;19; Dudeney 1970; Gar=
dner 1978;
 Cajori 1993; Conway and Guy 1996).
</p>
<p>
The special case <img src=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/images/equations=
